# tf.contrib.graph_editor.swap_inputs

### `tf.contrib.graph_editor.swap_inputs`

``` python
swap_inputs(
    sgv0,
    sgv1
)
```



Defined in [`tensorflow/contrib/graph_editor/reroute.py`](https://www.github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/r1.1/tensorflow/contrib/graph_editor/reroute.py).
